data.description: Welcome to this stunning home in the desirable Windward subdivision! This beautiful property boasts an impressive 6 bedrooms and 5 full bathrooms, perfect for accommodating families of all sizes or those who love to entertain.  Nestled on a private Cul-de-sac wooded lot, this residence offers tranquility and serenity amidst nature's embrace. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an impressive 2-story entryway that sets the tone throughout. Natural light floods the home, accentuating the beautiful hardwood floors and highlighting the meticulous attention to detail and open flow. The main level offers a spacious living room and a grand two-story family room, providing ample space for relaxation and entertaining. The oversized kitchen is a chef’s delight, featuring solid wood cabinets and offering wooded views that inspire culinary creativity. The oversized dining room is perfect for holiday dinners.   Upstairs, escape to the master suite with a generous master bath boasting a soaking tub and dual vanity. The additional bedrooms are equally impressive, with an en-suite or shared jack & jill bathroom for added convenience and comfort.   If you're looking for additional living space, the large basement has it all, a haven for entertainment, featuring a media room ideal for movie nights, exercise room, home office and a generously sized bedroom with a full en-suite bathroom, offering privacy and comfort for guests or family members. The possibilities are endless for customizing this space to suit your lifestyle.  Entertain and relax on the large deck where you can unwind and enjoy the serene surroundings. The private level yard is an outdoor oasis spanning over 3/4 of an acre is perfect for hosting gatherings, enjoying summer barbecues, or simply unwinding while surrounded by nature.  With easy access to the pool, lake, schools and the greenway walking tails. You are only a few miles to Avalon, Halcyon & Downtown Alpharetta making it an ideal location. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a truly exceptional home in Windward. Schedule your private tour today and experience the luxury and comfort that awaits you in this remarkable property.
